[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（ランターナの伝承って、やっぱり興味深い……\n　まだまだ、行ったことのない場所は多いわね――）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "失礼する。\nユリエ・クロッツェ、少し時間をもらえるか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "あなたは……\n私に、何か用？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "ランターナ王国から、君に頼みがある。\n君の手で『ランターナ紀行』を書いてくれないか",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "『ランターナ紀行』……紀行文？　\nどうして、私に？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "レスナから、君が旅の記録を付けていると聞いた。\nそして、その筆致が素晴らしいものであるとも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "先日、彼女たちによって、ランターナ王国と\nノーヴァ神聖国の国交が回復したのは知っているな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "そこで我々は、ランターナ大陸の外に向け、\nランターナについて記した本を用意しようと考えた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "経緯は分かった。\nでも私、ただのトレジャーハンターよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "君が書く文章には、人の心を動かす力がある――\n錬金術士レスナは、そう言っていた",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "それに君は異邦人だ。我々の文化にとらわれない、\n君の視点から見たランターナについて記してほしい",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……そんな大層なこと、私にできるかしら",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "君の妹ミルカからも話を聞き、その上で依頼している。\nもちろん、報酬も用意する",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……ランターナ各地を旅して、\n私が思ったこと、感じたことを書けばいいのね？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "ああ。美辞麗句は不要だ。\n君が見て感じた真実だけを書いてくれ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "……引き受けてくれるか？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "断る理由はなさそうだけど、\nすぐに返事はできない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "6932496336129827816",
		"text": "……少し考えさせて",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ブラッド",
		"romanized_name": "Brad",
		"model_path_hash": "5720487083297329396",
		"text": "分かった。\n良い返事を期待している",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（普段からの旅の記録が、まさか\n　こんな形で執筆の機会に繋がるなんて……）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "（『ランターナ紀行』……受けてみようかしら）",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ユリエ・クロッツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Jurie Crotze",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "一匹狼のトレジャーハンター。\n旅の経験を冒険譚に重ねて、詳細に記録を付けている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8415011553540267009",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "ブラッドリー・カーン",
		"romanized_name": "Bradley Khan",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "通称「ブラッド」。ランターナ王国錬金爵。\nロマン不在のランターナにて、オルペウスを支えている",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "916521448425681550",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]